Class SeatHold

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mybooking.entities.SeatHold

  • public class SeatHold
extends Object
    This class models the information on the Seats being held for a customer;
    The seatHold is identified by a Seat Hold Identifier.
    The Customer holding the seats is identified using an email id.
